/*Task: Interaction Success Rate
Objective: Determine the success rate of interactions (percentage of "Delivered"messages) for each communication channel.
Required Output: Channel, Success_Rate
Tables Used: interview.interactions
Uses CASE statement to identify 'Delivered' interactions..
Divides delivered interactions by total interactions per channel.
Multiplies by 100 to get percentage.
*/
SELECT
i.channel,
SUM(CASE WHEN i.status = 'Delivered' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / COUNT(*) * 100 AS Success_Rate
FROM
interview.interactions i
GROUP BY i.channel;
